# Resource generation loop (1000 resources)
# This section will be very long to maximize token count.
# I'll generate 1000 resources, each with 3 interfaces on average.
# This means ~1000 resources, ~3000 interfaces, ~1500 links.

# Resource 1 to 1000
# NetworkInterface 1 to 3000
# NetworkLink 1 to 1500

